items.preText: And Jarvis pulls out at the last moment. Touches his hamstring immediately, but is ready to bowl again. Oh no, this are worrying signs for Zimbabwe, he pulls out for the second time. He is walking off. Tiripano to replace Jarvis
items.text: short of length, pulled straight to short midwicket
items.shortText: Tiripano to Liton Das, no run

items.text: length outside off, steered towards backward point where a fumble allows a single
on the pads this time and flicked away in the air, but falls well short of the man at deep square leg, only a single
down the track to a short of length ball, it was wide as well and Liton had to reach for it in the end, toe-end it towards short midwicket
items.shortText: Tiripano to Liton Das, no run

items.text: once again use of feet but guided nicely towards third man this time
on the pads and flicked away in the air. The square leg fielder messes it up altogether, drops the catch and lets the ball roll to the fence
items.shortText: Tiripano to Imrul Kayes, FOUR runs

items.text: finally a wicket for Zimbabwe! down the track and looks to chip it over mid-off. But Liton doesn't get his timing right and a good tumbling catch to his left by Zhuwao

dismissal.text: Liton Das c Zhuwao b Chatara 4 (14b 0x4 0x6) SR: 28.57

items.preText: Fazle Mahmud is the new batsman but he is at the non-striker's end
items.text: short of length and pulled awkwardly towards square leg, falls short of the fielder
another bouncer, but it sails over the batsman who ducks under it
items.shortText: Chatara to Fazle Mahmud, no run

items.text: fuller on stumps this time, pushed towards mid-on
items.shortText: Chatara to Fazle Mahmud, no run

items.text: length ball, comes forward and defends it on the off side
items.shortText: Chatara to Fazle Mahmud, no run

items.text: a lifter there from Chatara and Bangladesh lose their second wicket. The debutant departs for a duck as he fends at this one and Taylor takes a one-handed catch, jumping to his left

dismissal.text: Fazle Mahmud c †Taylor b Chatara 0 (4b 0x4 0x6) SR: 0.00

items.text: on the pads, Imrul misses the flick, an appeal for lbw but it was heading down
items.shortText: Tiripano to Imrul Kayes, 1 leg bye

items.text: fuller outside off, Mushfiqur goes for the drive, gets an inside edge to fine leg, not the best of the ways to get off the mark
fuller on pads and tucked away to the left of mid-on for a quick single
back of length outside off, stays in his crease and defends solidly
items.shortText: Tiripano to Mushfiqur Rahim, no run

items.text: short of length, coming into the right-hander, steered towards third man
fuller outside off, driven but straight to the fielder at mid-off
items.shortText: Tiripano to Imrul Kayes, no run

items.text: length ball, comes forward and pushes it towards mid-on for a quick single, makes it comfortably in the end
back of length, in the rib cage, tucked away towards square leg
length outside off, in the channel, left alone
items.shortText: Chatara to Mushfiqur Rahim, no run

items.text: on the pads this time, flicked away towards backward square leg for a single
slower one but down the leg side, that needs to be bowled again
short of length this time but once again down the leg side, another wide
length ball, into the body this time, defended
items.shortText: Chatara to Imrul Kayes, no run
